            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the gnocchi is crispy, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and <strong>chopped rosemary</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant – this is your <strong>garlic & rosemary gnocchi</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
