    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>garlic & rosemary gnocchi</strong> to the pan with the sausage meat and give everything a good mix up until coated in the sauce</p><p>Stir through <strong>half </strong>of your <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong> (save the rest for garnish!) and season with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>– this is your<strong> creamy sausage</strong>, <strong>rosemary & garlic gnocchi</strong></p>",
